# Gforce API - Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values.

```
# JWT secret - change this to a long random string in production
JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-a-long-random-string

# Office staff password
OFFICE_PASSWORD=office123

# SQLite database path (leave default for single-server deploy)
DB_PATH=./gforce.db

# Port (default 3000, use PROCESS_ENV_PORT on Render)
PORT=3000
```

For adding pilots, the database seeds Brooke with PIN 1234 on first run.
To add more pilots, connect to the SQLite db and insert:

```sql
INSERT INTO pilots (id, name, pin_hash) VALUES (
  lower(hex(randomblob(16))),
  'Pilot Name',
  '<bcrypt hash of PIN>'
);
```

Generate a bcrypt hash in Node:
```js
require('bcryptjs').hashSync('1234', 10)
```
